title: Streamlined Mythbusters Complete (as of June 23rd, 2013)
description:
This is a compilation of all current(as of June 23, 2013) streamlined Mythbusters episodes. These 'Streamline' edits run shorter because they are missing teasers, cartoons, flashbacks, repetition, idents, history lessons, fun facts, "we're experts", and anything else that slows down the show.

This is Mythbusters, the way it's meant to be seen.

All credit for these edits goes to reddit users Postdarwin, Runke, Myfbusted, MrTwinkles, Realblublu, Ram27, and DeLoRtEd1. Postdarwin created the subreddit /r/smyths and you should go there if you want to find more streamlined episodes.
